{
  "stem": "13251.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't police.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the railroad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And another thing that I had-- hadn't mentioned earlier-- even though my brother was older than me, as a child, he was-- he was not a well child.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I kind of felt protective of him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, my wife-- I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- my mother needed to call my dad to straighten out this problem.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know if it was coming with money or what.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But-- so there was no phones in those days, not in that area.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, so I-- my mother sent me to get my dad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, remember, I ran all the way, because I knew there was-- it was something very important.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I brought my dad-- bailed us out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, I ran all the way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "OK, that's just some of  the things I remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, in fact, before they enrolled my brother to-- to school, we were going to like Jewish preschool.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They call that-- what do they call that?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Cheder, cheder, cheder.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They call that, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, you know, it's usually-- usually-- it's always, it's rabbis that train your religious studies from a very young age.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And for some reason, I have-- it's almost funny, I remember big horse flies.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maybe the-- you know, it wasn't  a very clean area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it was-- it's funny how things stick in your mind-- like god, these big guys.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were very Orthodox. yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember one time-- like, it's traditional for Jewish people on-- on-- on Sabbath, they had these traditional dishes that they used to serve-- almost every Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
